<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٧٢٦ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1588">أَبُو الْيَمَانِ: </a>أَخْبَرَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2785">شُعَيْبُ بْنُ أَبِي حَمْزَةَ: </a>قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6509">نَافِعٌ: </a>كَانَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3807">ابْنُ عُمَرَ </a><span class="special">﵄</span> يَقُولُ: <span class="c2">«حَلَقَ رَسُولُ اللهِ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> فِي حَجَّتِهِ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>